Comment: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.07,op jp,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.00,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Comment: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.56,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Comment: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Tell me what do you want from me
Comment: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.60,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Comment: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.46,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Looking for the escape from pain
Comment: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.86,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Comment: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.30,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Comment: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.06,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Comment: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.60,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Comment: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.96,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Comment: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.53,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}May be it's already too late to regain
Comment: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.90,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Comment: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Ever again
Comment: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.70,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Comment: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough
Comment: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:07.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Comment: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Comment: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.56,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}we'll make it in the end
Comment: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:20.86,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Comment: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I know who I am
Comment: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:10.99,op ch,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.00,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命运将我们引领至此 并看着我跳战不可能
Comment: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.56,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}感觉我堕入了谎言的火焰中
Comment: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}说出你对我的要求
Comment: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.60,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}尽力不去走回头路
Comment: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.46,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探求走出痛苦的方法
Comment: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.86,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我合十双手去祈求不必牺牲
Comment: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.30,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这是我和你的希望所订下的约定
Comment: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.06,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在时机成熟前做好出击的准备
Comment: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.60,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去追赶那个浮现出来的黑影
Comment: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.96,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}放弃那个让我单独一人的理由
Comment: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.53,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}或许这已经太迟
Comment: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.90,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要舍去作为命运的那道光
Comment: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}没有下次
Comment: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.70,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}若我能修补错误并将你救出苦海
Comment: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这并不足以
Comment: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:07.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}并不足以让我打破这世界的规则
Comment: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我绝不离开你 绝不想失去你
Comment: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.56,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我们来结束这一切
Comment: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:20.86,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}别再退缩 这辈子我不会跟随别人
Comment: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我知道自己是谁
Comment: 0,0:27:30.04,0:27:30.08,ed jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:50.53,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}壊れないように優しく抱いて　溶けて涙流す
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.10,0:28:01.73,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そんな氷の人形みたいに なれないから
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.16,0:28:15.96,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}もう逃げない　知りたいの　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:17.66,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}―I believe…believe in you―
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.66,0:28:21.76,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}きっと一番の約束の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.76,0:28:26.16,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}痛いくらい握って離さない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.46,0:28:32.10,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}わがままな今連れて　誰のものでもない未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:34.80,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そこから始めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.80,0:28:45.36,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}空を掴む(夢の欠片)　祈りの手を(指先まで)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:50.43,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}伸ばすかぎり(生けるかぎり)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.43,0:28:58.50,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そこに本当はあるの
Comment: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:24.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:50.53,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}小心翼翼地温柔抱着 使它流下熔化的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.10,0:28:01.73,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}我可没法成为那样的冰雪人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.16,0:28:15.96,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}我再也不会逃避 我想要知道变强的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:17.66,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.66,0:28:21.76,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}将第一个约定的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.76,0:28:26.16,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}紧握到疼痛 绝不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.46,0:28:32.10,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}带着任性的现在 前往不属于任何人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:34.80,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}从那里开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.80,0:28:45.36,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}抓紧天空(梦想的碎片) 祈愿的手(直到指尖)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:50.43,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}只要还能够伸出(只要仍活着)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.43,0:28:58.50,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3)}那里就会有真物在
